name: Garden of Goldenlup Pt.3
description: The Goldenlup fruit is a legendary fruit that was first planted by the celestial tribe. the process of growing this fruit until the harvest period takes 50 days from flowering. The fruit has many benefits from being a food source, the skin can be brewed for relaxation. While the dried Goldenlup seeds can be used to cure all diseases except death. Pancho (the caterpillar), Mushi (the Mushroom Head), and the Iki teach humans to grow crops and learn about medicine.
